            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="" resp="#automat">letter from Briton Riviere to E. M. Bonham Carter, 26 June 1871</ref>. CD refers to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1312.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Elinor Mary Bonham-Carter</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="" resp="#automat">letter from Briton Riviere to E. M. Bonham Carter, 26 June 1871</ref> and n. 2.</note>
        </div>        
            
